Launch Shadow Clone with:
- Project plan: ./custom.md
- Workspace: ./project
- 5 specialized sub-agents
- Balanced wave strategy
- 3 execution waves
Create background agents for each team role.

# With dynamic project creation
Launch Shadow Clone with dynamic project creation:
- Project: Build a comprehensive SaaS platform with multi-tenant architecture, payment integration, and admin dashboard
- Workspace: ./project
- 5 specialized sub-agents
- Balanced wave strategy
